00:26:59.729 --> 00:27:01.270
But at the same
time, it's like, it's

00:27:01.270 --> 00:27:03.420
kind of like it is
ridiculous to be just sitting

00:27:03.420 --> 00:27:06.850
around and forcing people
to talk about this in we're

00:27:06.850 --> 00:27:09.040
in the year 2016 or whatever.

00:27:09.040 --> 00:27:11.180
So it's just that mix of
both I guess, but that's

00:27:11.180 --> 00:27:14.090
